# Story Reader (Next.js)

Read `story_reader/CLAUDE.md` before UI changes.

## CRITICAL — do not run heavy commands

Machine has limited RAM/GPU. **Never run** in agent:

- `npx tsc --noEmit`, `npm run build`, `next build`, `npm run dev`
- Headless browser / Playwright / Puppeteer

Verify by reading files and grepping. Ask user to run tsc/build if needed.

## Stack

Next.js 15 App Router, React 19, Redux Toolkit, React Query, Three.js (dynamic import only).

## Styling

- Global: `app/globals.css` (append-only cascade)
- Reader: `app/stories/[storyId]/chapters/[chapterNumber]/reader.css`
- Do not introduce a conflicting design system — follow `DESIGN.md`

